We visited the Khao Kheow, Pattaya today. While Reyansh is totally opposed to the idea of a Zoo. He agreed for this one coz most of the animals are rescued. Khao Khew also supports breeding, conservation and educating the tourists about these animals 🐾 It was a super fun day feeding Elephant’s, Penguins, Orangutans and other animals. Proud of this generation for teaching us that fun doesn’t have to come at the cost of ethics 🫡 @khaokheow.zoo 
.
.
#KhaoKhew #OpenSafari #SafariDay #ThailandDiaries
